# Build Bible V2 — Chapter 9 (I18N / L10N / Regionalization)

Spec: `docs/11_BUILD_BIBLE_V2_CHAPTER_09_I18N.md`

## Rules

- Format money with `formatWorkspaceMoney` / `useWorkspaceMoney().formatMoney` — never hardcode currency symbols.
- Format dates/times with `formatAppDate*` or workspace provider helpers — never assume `en-US` / German display.
- Format numbers/percents with `formatAppNumber` / `formatAppPercent`.
- Organization regional settings are the primary source; user prefs may override display timezone/date/time.
- Backend storage stays UTC / ISO / numeric. Presentation owns locale formatting.
- Do not invent machine translation; use the message catalog scaffold for future packs.
- Never weaken auth, RBAC, RLS, or Paddle billing behaviour.

## This chapter

- Do not commit, push, or deploy from Chapter 9 work.
